rows.label: qst703102_msg0001
rows.name:
Need friends to collect Apple Lamps
and Alloy Sheeting.

rows.label: qst703102_msg0002
rows.name:
Might be able to get hands on by
taking apart machines littered
around Gula.

rows.label: qst703102_msg0003
rows.name:
Then can dive into Cloud Sea with
Silver Cylinder on back, and show
world what Dudan all about!

rows.label: qst703102_msg0101
rows.name:
While Dudan going about salvaging,
almost became lunch of urchon!

rows.label: qst703102_msg0102
rows.name:
Dudan made for surface as fast
as wings could paddle, but urchon
follow all way to surface!

rows.label: qst703102_msg0103
rows.name:
Only option is to fend off! Request
assistance to take Dudan off menu?

rows.label: qst703102_msg0201
rows.name:
Would like friends to open treasure
fished up from Cloud Sea.

rows.label: qst703102_msg0202
rows.name:
Dudan not expecting monsters
to jump out or any such thing...

rows.label: qst703102_msg0203
rows.name:
Me just feel friends deserve to
experience thrill of opening, since
have done all the work.

rows.label: qst703102_msg0301
rows.name:
At long last! Dudan finally get paws
on Gravitonic Clutch!

rows.label: qst703102_msg0302
rows.name:
Now to take to partner and finish
off project...

rows.label: qst703102_msg0303
rows.name:
If get hold of certain thing in great
number, Dudan can say goodbye to
life slaving under Cloud Sea!

rows.label: qst703102_msg0304
rows.name:
Dudan return to Iira now. Greatest
of thanking to friends!

rows.label: qst703102_msg0306
rows.name:
Dudan leave collectibles here as
reward, like promised. Hope will
come in handy!
